How to query the answer, the final product can be deploied in one computer or 
serveral within or not the same computer as the JAVA client.

-- install dependency --
pip install synonyms mysql-connector-python

-- run --
python ret.py

-- usage --
http://localhost:44442/?q=<unquoted string>&pid=<unquoted string>&compid=<unquoted string>
  -- q      : query string
  -- pid    : product id
  -- compid : company id
  -- <unquoted string> : string without quotes or double quotes
  -- example           : localhost:44442/?q=你好进水了&pid=product_x&compid=x
